sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / Dashboard
    participant API as API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432 TCP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Argo as Argo Workflows
    participant Driver as Driver<br/>(Argo step init)
    participant Cache as Cache Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLMD as ML Metadata<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant Launcher as Launcher<br/>(Argo step main)
    participant UserCode as User Container
    participant ObjStore as MinIO / S3<br/>9000/443 TCP

    Note over Client,ObjStore: Flow 1: Pipeline Execution

    Client->>API: POST /apis/v2beta1/runs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    API->>DB: Store run metadata<br/>Username/Password
    API->>K8s: Create Argo Workflow CR<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8s->>Argo: Workflow scheduled

    Argo->>Driver: Init container starts<br/>(local process)
    Driver->>MLMD: Resolve input artifacts<br/>gRPC 8080, Optional TLS
    Driver->>API: Cache fingerprint lookup<br/>gRPC 8887, Optional TLS
    Driver->>K8s: Read ConfigMaps<br/>HTTPS 6443, SA Token
    Driver-->>Argo: Pod spec patches

    Argo->>Launcher: Main container starts<br/>(local process)
    Launcher->>UserCode: Execute user code<br/>(subprocess)
    UserCode-->>Launcher: Outputs / artifacts
    Launcher->>MLMD: Publish output metadata<br/>gRPC 8080, Optional TLS
    Launcher->>ObjStore: Upload artifacts<br/>HTTP(S) 9000/443, Access Key
    Launcher->>API: Record cache execution<br/>gRPC 8887, Optional TLS

    Note over Client,ObjStore: Flow 2: Persistence Agent Sync

    participant PA as Persistence Agent

    PA->>K8s: Watch Workflows &<br/>ScheduledWorkflows<br/>HTTPS 6443, SA Token
    K8s-->>PA: Workflow status events
    PA->>API: Persist state via gRPC<br/>8887/TCP, SA Token

    Note over Client,ObjStore: Flow 3: Scheduled Workflow Trigger

    participant SWF as SWF Controller

    SWF->>K8s: Watch ScheduledWorkflow CRs<br/>HTTPS 6443, SA Token
    K8s-->>SWF: Schedule trigger event
    alt Direct Workflow creation
        SWF->>K8s: Create Argo Workflow<br/>HTTPS 6443, SA Token
    else API-based run creation
        SWF->>API: CreateRun via gRPC<br/>8887/TCP, SA Token
    end
